race.description: Westpac Rescue Helicopter Service Xmas Cup Hcp
race.comment: DARK CHILL (10) came out fast from the outside gate before folding up in the straight when ninth over 1600m at Eagle Farm in C3 class. Gets a better set-up today and anywhere near his best can win this. LOVEWILLCOMELATER (4) just over three weeks between runs when a surprise on-pace winner over 1400m at Randwick in Highway class. Can continue the winning momentum despite drawing out. BOLD HOI HO (8) dominant winner two-back, before failing to get into the contest from the sticky draw when tenth over 1620m at Grafton. Senior rider hops aboard and stays in the calculations. NAILS AND PRIDE (9) model of consistency this time in and looks to have excellent each-way claims. Strong through the line when fifth over 1300m at Ballina. Respect.
